data.title: "Thomas & Friends Storytime" The Story of Percy the Small Engine (TV Episode 2020)
data.meta_description: The Story of Percy the Small Engine: Directed by John Gilluley. With Mark Moraghan. When the big engines refuse to come out of the shed, Sir Topham Hatt buys a little tank engine called Percy. Not long after, Percy gets a fright on the main line.
